Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.63,0:00:10.64,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.98,0:00:19.16,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.34,0:00:31.46,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.35,0:00:35.55,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.75,0:00:38.67,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,This is yours, Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.90,0:00:55.25,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.25,0:00:56.91,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I do! I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.39,0:01:00.66,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This is mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.26,0:01:05.92,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead, try it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.38,0:01:15.02,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,And while we're at it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.51,0:01:31.77,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Looks good on you.\NDon't you think so, Mister Yami?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.58,0:01:34.44,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,He looks pretty bland.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.13,0:01:40.43,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,And now, you're officially a member of \Nthe Magic Knights Squad, the Black Bulls!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.95,0:01:45.14,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,You better work hard not to shame \NMister Yami or the Black Bulls!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.41,0:01:51.71,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks! It's a pleasure \Nto work with all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.97,0:02:03.30,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.30,0:02:04.18,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.18,0:02:06.94,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be more careful next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.29,0:02:09.94,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,The captain just told you to shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.03,0:02:13.51,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,That's the other new recruit?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.34,0:02:19.86,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What an insect.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.61,0:02:45.51,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,750)}The Other New Recruit
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.64,0:02:49.74,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Grey words can't make anything happen
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.74,0:02:52.24,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, yeah I know
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.24,0:02:57.66,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wishing to fly freely across the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.66,0:03:00.00,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I dreamed it all my life
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.00,0:03:03.53,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Step by step I go, though \Nit's a doubtful world 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.53,0:03:05.55,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't care how much I fall
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.55,0:03:08.77,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Instinct is my guide, I never give up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.17,0:03:15.24,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,To faraway future, I burst out running
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.57,0:03:20.59,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Go beyond even the unseen fears
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.93,0:03:25.82,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The vision I had, so I can be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.08,0:03:31.09,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday I will write the next page
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.37,0:03:34.46,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,You are my hope
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:37.48,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Like that page from someday
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:39.72,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to meet you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.13,0:03:42.81,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I call this a miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.87,0:03:52.83,sign_29843_252_Black_Bulls__Bas,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Black Bulls' Base
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.01,0:03:59.21,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,This is your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.21,0:04:00.22,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.22,0:04:04.58,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Isn't it depressing \Nhow small and filthy it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.89,0:04:08.85,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, my room is twice as big—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.51,0:04:11.97,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,My own room!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.97,0:04:13.10,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,He's actually moved?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.10,0:04:16.09,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I-I've never had my own room!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.09,0:04:20.77,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,At the church, we all shared a room,\Nso we'd sleep lined up next to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.29,0:04:23.69,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hi-yah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.69,0:04:25.78,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna get you {\i1}so{\i0} clean!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.78,0:04:28.69,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Until you're all sparkly and shiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.69,0:04:30.74,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Better get scrubbin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.74,0:04:33.05,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,You're free to do whatever \Nuntil we get a mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.87,0:04:36.00,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, by the way, Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.35,0:04:37.42,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.78,0:04:39.51,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you write letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.51,0:04:40.56,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.56,0:04:42.61,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,To everyone at that church of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:47.55,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,They're your family, right? I'm sure they're \Nworried about how things turned out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.55,0:04:49.04,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.04,0:04:51.18,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make anyone worry about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.51,0:04:54.56,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,That's how to be a real man. See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.74,0:04:58.05,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,If you need anything, come see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.05,0:05:00.61,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Right! Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.98,0:05:08.28,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This is my first castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.37,0:05:12.73,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to climb my way up \Nto Wizard King from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.38,0:05:21.05,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to lose. Got it, Yuno?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.61,0:05:26.13,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,How unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.79,0:05:29.05,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,This room is wasted on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.58,0:05:35.18,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, I'll be lecturing you \Non your duties as a Magic Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.03,0:05:39.12,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather not be your instructor,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.12,0:05:42.26,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,but the captain ordered me to do so, \Nand as such, I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.37,0:05:44.39,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.39,0:05:45.26,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,It's Yuno.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.97,0:05:50.16,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I have a name, and it's Yuno, Klaus.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.06,0:05:52.41,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your senior.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.13,0:05:56.35,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,You'll address me with respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.35,0:05:57.41,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.66,0:05:59.73,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.05,0:06:31.91,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.92,0:06:46.20,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, Yuno!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.90,0:06:50.72,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,He made it into the Magic Knights!\N He's truly our pride!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.21,0:06:53.09,main,Arlu,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.09,0:06:54.01,main,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.42,0:06:56.89,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,I have to let the whole village know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.39,0:07:02.02,main,Rekka,0000,0000,0000,,So, Sister, what does the \Nletter from Asta say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.02,0:07:05.40,main,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,Man, his handwriting sucks. \NWhen's he coming home?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.01,0:07:08.87,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to cheer him up \Nwhen he comes back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.87,0:07:11.92,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure even Asta would \Nbe depressed about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.92,0:07:14.66,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have a super tato party.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.53,0:07:17.41,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,He says he passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.59,0:07:21.42,main,Father and rekka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.70,0:07:24.08,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Asta passed, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.39,0:07:26.17,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.65,0:07:28.34,main,Father and nash,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.94,0:07:32.68,main,Rekka,0000,0000,0000,,Wow... He really passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.20,0:07:36.92,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then I guess he won't be coming home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.92,0:07:40.03,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,I see... So they both passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.03,0:07:42.50,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'm going to tell the whole village!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.50,0:07:46.57,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first bit of good news we've\Ngotten since Hage Village was founded!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.51,0:07:46.57,top,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.04,0:07:51.03,main,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So Asta passed, too... I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.78,0:07:54.79,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Asta, Yuno, congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.30,0:07:57.05,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Keep doing your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.22,0:08:13.38,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.66,0:08:21.99,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Let's do thi—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.02,0:08:24.93,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.43,0:08:28.11,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Was this pillar here yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.11,0:08:30.92,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, newbie. Did you sleep well?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.92,0:08:35.45,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, g-good morning!\NUm, sir, about this pillar...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.19,0:08:37.85,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.85,0:08:40.51,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it was here yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.51,0:08:45.79,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about a pillar. The base \Nitself changes its shape all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.79,0:08:47.47,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.47,0:08:49.09,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. You'll get used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.67,0:08:51.63,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.63,0:08:54.02,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.02,0:08:55.22,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:57.38,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,You're in for a treat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.38,0:09:01.56,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I'll personally show you around \Nthe Black Bulls' super cool base!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.17,0:09:04.29,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Follow me, Shrimpsta!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.29,0:09:06.63,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Got it, Mr. Sunglasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.06,0:09:09.44,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Moron! You mean the Great Magna!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.44,0:09:11.66,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Moron! The Great Magna!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.66,0:09:12.99,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need the "moron" part!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.46,0:09:16.36,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,This is the cafeteria!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.03,0:09:20.49,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think? It's stupidly huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.49,0:09:22.12,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! It's really big!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:26.18,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,This is the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.39,0:09:29.38,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.38,0:09:34.33,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,This kind of heat is nothing to \Na member of the Black Bulls!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.33,0:09:36.57,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're getting out already?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.57,0:09:40.62,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, not yet! I'm not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.62,0:09:43.85,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot. I want to add cold water. \NHanging out naked is nice, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.30,0:09:47.54,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Over there are all the girls' rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.54,0:09:50.07,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,If any of us guys go in,\Nyou'll be killed by trap magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.07,0:09:51.52,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.52,0:09:53.98,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,And this is... the toilet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.90,0:09:55.78,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.78,0:09:58.28,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.65,0:10:03.97,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,This is the beasts' room!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.97,0:10:05.68,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.68,0:10:07.39,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,This is Mister Yami's hobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.93,0:10:08.85,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.85,0:10:09.88,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.41,0:10:14.44,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you have the duty of \Ntaking care of all the animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.44,0:10:15.27,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.27,0:10:20.34,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,It's a very honorable role. I really don't \Nwant to let you have it, but I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.34,0:10:22.26,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Feed 'em twice a day,\Nin the morning and at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.26,0:10:23.98,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.39,0:10:25.60,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.98,0:10:29.74,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,There, there... Here, eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.65,0:10:35.07,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,This is the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.07,0:10:35.98,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.35,0:10:39.91,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,This is the playroom.\NYou can have plenty of fun here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.91,0:10:41.20,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.79,0:10:45.85,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Try to keep up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.85,0:10:48.15,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.15,0:10:49.71,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.73,0:10:52.55,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.05,0:10:54.96,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Magna?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.54,0:11:02.16,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,A Black Bulls robe. Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.16,0:11:04.89,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Asta. That's your colleague.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.31,0:11:07.41,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,She's the other new recruit this year!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.41,0:11:08.85,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? My colleague?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.85,0:11:10.39,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I love the sound of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.71,0:11:13.15,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I'm Asta, from Hage Village!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.55,0:11:16.32,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do our best together! \NIt's nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.67,0:11:22.73,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't give you permission to speak to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.15,0:11:26.83,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I barely sense any mana \Nfrom you, you lowly insect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.83,0:11:28.12,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Insect?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.60,0:11:29.58,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Lowly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.59,0:11:34.29,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Noelle Silva. I belong \Nto the royal family of this kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.29,0:11:35.93,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.93,0:11:40.80,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,R-R-R-Royal family?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.33,0:11:52.74,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I do beg your pardon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.74,0:11:57.09,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm but a puny insect that someone \Ncould blow away just by breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.55,0:11:59.99,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.49,0:12:01.72,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.72,0:12:03.49,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you calling an insect, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.49,0:12:06.70,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We're supposed to be \Ncolleagues as Magic Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.70,0:12:09.07,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares if you're royalty?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.07,0:12:12.91,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Asta! You tell her!\NStatus means nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.94,0:12:15.21,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.53,0:12:17.84,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,How do you figure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.70,0:12:22.59,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Are foolish peasants unable to \Nunderstand this with words alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.69,0:12:26.51,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll have to show you with the \Ndifference between our magical powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.26,0:12:28.35,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.51,0:12:38.19,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Know your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.75,0:12:42.28,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I won't make it in ti—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.94,0:12:54.01,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.01,0:12:56.83,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,You little bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.83,0:13:01.46,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,You've got some nerve! What do you \Nthink you're doing to your senior?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.96,0:13:04.77,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,You were just standing in the wrong spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.77,0:13:07.47,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Who gave you permission to stand there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.80,0:13:11.21,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.87,0:13:12.28,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you little...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.28,0:13:14.48,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your senior!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.48,0:13:16.53,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm royalty!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.53,0:13:18.04,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.04,0:13:22.07,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if you're royalty or the \NSilver Eagles' captain's little sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.07,0:13:22.94,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.94,0:13:28.30,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, the only person who'd accept \Na spoiled brat like you is Mister Yami!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.30,0:13:30.40,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Be more thankful, you moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.40,0:13:35.04,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I held back because you're a girl, but now \NI'm gonna have to initiate you, too, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.51,0:13:46.05,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Like I want to be in this pathetic squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.68,0:13:47.77,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,You little...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.53,0:13:51.35,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What the hell do \Nyou think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.03,0:13:55.85,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares about the Black Bulls?\NI don't need that filthy thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.17,0:13:59.27,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,This is the absolute \Nworst Magic Knights Squad,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.27,0:14:01.86,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,and it's not where royalty \Nlike myself belongs!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.86,0:14:05.90,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! Apologize to \Nthe robe and Mister Yami!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.38,0:14:12.77,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Apologize! Apologize! Apologize, \Ndamn it! You moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.95,0:14:11.87,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The robe I worked so hard \Nto get... She just...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.01,0:14:18.74,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck was her problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.37,0:14:27.11,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't find the toilet \Nand ended up outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.03,0:14:30.26,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.58,0:14:38.60,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What? What? What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.61,0:14:55.54,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.31,0:15:08.70,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.26,0:15:11.51,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't it go the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.61,0:15:16.19,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I want it to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:23.27,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'm just...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.57,0:15:30.34,flashback,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, the youngest of the Silva family \Ncan't even control her magical powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.34,0:15:34.53,flashback,Voice 2,0000,0000,0000,,Who would have thought someone like that \Nwould be born into the royal family?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.53,0:15:37.82,flashback,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that flimsy little grimoire?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:40.41,flashback,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really royalty?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.77,0:15:46.13,flashback,Nebra,0000,0000,0000,,It's just pathetic that you can't \Neven control your powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.13,0:15:49.42,flashback,Nebra,0000,0000,0000,,It disgusts me that you're my little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.34,0:15:57.10,flashback,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,I will not have someone as shameful \Nas you in the Silver Eagles.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.75,0:16:02.94,flashback,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,Why couldn't you have died \Ninstead of our mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.94,0:16:05.15,flashback,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,You're a complete failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.98,0:16:13.78,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a failure!\NI'll make them acknowledge me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.46,0:16:24.79,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I guess she's got it rough, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.66,0:16:29.55,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.39,0:16:32.00,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Insect?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.00,0:16:33.78,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,H-How long have you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.78,0:16:36.05,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be mocked again...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.05,0:16:37.08,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.08,0:16:42.71,flashbackitalics,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,I will not have someone as shameful \Nas you in the Silver Eagles.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.31,0:16:44.82,flashbackitalicstop,Nebra,0000,0000,0000,,It's just pathetic that you can't \Neven control your powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.73,0:16:45.81,flashbackitalics,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really royalty?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.81,0:16:47.00,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,N...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.00,0:16:47.81,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,N?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.49,0:16:49.74,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.97,0:17:10.27,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,All done taking a dump.\NGuess I'll go back to bed now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.19,0:17:13.76,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.36,0:17:36.68,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.68,0:17:37.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.64,0:17:39.20,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,This is insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.59,0:17:42.04,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's magic is out of control.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.04,0:17:44.25,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Such immense magical power...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.25,0:17:46.61,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,This is gonna get bad if \Nwe don't do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.13,0:18:01.66,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,If we attack it with magic, \Nshe might not make it out alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.66,0:18:04.35,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Could you use your spatial magic\Nto scoop just her up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.78,0:18:09.28,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't be ridiculous. \NI can't get near that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.28,0:18:14.36,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Right. If only we had someone who \Ncould nullify magical powers...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.36,0:18:17.25,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.25,0:18:20.43,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You came flying by at the perfect time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.43,0:18:21.88,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.88,0:18:24.95,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Could you go take care of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.51,0:18:26.87,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.87,0:18:28.57,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.57,0:18:33.49,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. How am I supposed to get \Nover there, though? I can't fly...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.49,0:18:35.09,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Quit yer yapping.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.83,0:18:41.51,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Now is the time when you need \Nto go beyond your limits!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.77,0:19:08.04,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.03,0:19:16.63,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'm alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.43,0:19:21.42,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,That was so much fun, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.45,0:19:22.93,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez. Now I'm all wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.90,0:19:25.68,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for that spatial magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.29,0:19:27.85,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.85,0:19:30.14,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.14,0:19:31.28,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.90,0:19:33.02,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:39.86,flashback,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,You failure...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.59,0:19:44.03,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,They're going to mock me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.62,0:19:49.04,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.47,0:19:55.34,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,...have some insane magical powers!\NThat's so awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.65,0:19:56.96,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.96,0:20:02.22,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any magical powers, \Nso I'm jealous, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.69,0:20:05.29,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,If you train so you can learn to control them,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.29,0:20:07.85,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,you'll be invincible, Noelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.53,0:20:12.85,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Insec—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.66,0:20:16.11,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.74,0:20:20.49,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna keep doing my \Nbest so I won't lose, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.96,0:20:24.70,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Really? You just couldn't \Ncontrol your magical powers?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.24,0:20:28.05,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,You should've told me earlier, \Nyou royal failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.65,0:20:34.37,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,We're the Black Bulls.\NWe're a whole group of failures!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.55,0:20:43.72,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,No one cares if you have \Na flaw or two, you idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.13,0:20:49.77,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, thank goodness you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.77,0:20:54.27,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I know a great pasta place.\NWant to go sometime?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.27,0:20:57.96,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Before that, you should try this. 'Kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.96,0:21:00.10,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,That was amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.10,0:21:03.69,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,If anything, the one thing I'm great \Nat is controlling magical powers,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.69,0:21:05.52,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,so I'll help you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.52,0:21:08.50,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you some womanly techniques, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.50,0:21:12.58,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you how much of an \Nangel my little sister Marie is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.03,0:21:13.29,top,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start out as friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.35,0:21:19.54,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.59,0:21:22.55,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do our best together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.78,0:21:34.05,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pleasure to work with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.08,0:21:51.29,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can escape from here
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.14,0:21:58.04,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Once again in the small closed off classroom
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.16,0:22:06.02,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The star of the class was shining yet again
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.28,0:22:12.73,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,They shine so bright that I close my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.12,0:22:16.73,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I've thought many times
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.73,0:22:19.65,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,That the revolution was within my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.29,0:22:27.38,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it strange? If you want \Nto laugh, go ahead and laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.89,0:22:34.86,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest of us who were left \Nbehind wanted to become something
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.86,0:22:41.66,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We repeat the same morning over and over
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.09,0:22:49.00,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one who \Ncan choose your tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.00,0:22:53.17,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go beyond our current selves
