Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.13,0:23:11.53,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.78,0:23:15.79,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(523,1)}Honor Me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.79,0:23:14.58,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Honor Me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.77,0:23:19.73,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I am Noelle Silva, and I am a royal (ouzoku).
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.96,0:23:21.80,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,A bandit (sanzoku)?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.80,0:23:23.75,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling a bandit?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.33,0:23:26.46,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a royal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.46,0:23:28.53,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,A pirate (kaizoku)?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.53,0:23:30.47,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling a pirate?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.47,0:23:32.92,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a royal!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.92,0:23:34.33,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Family (Kazoku)?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.34,0:23:37.13,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.37,0:23:41.37,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Our first mission as Magic Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.37,0:23:44.86,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'll kick ass and go \Nstraight to being Wizard King!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.86,0:23:47.15,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? The mission is to hunt boars?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.54,0:23:51.05,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 8:\N"Go! Go! First Mission."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.65,0:23:55.00,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 8\N\N{\fs18}Go! Go! First Mission
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.05,0:23:53.70,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not giving up is my magic!
